Job title : Data mining analyst description 
Job description
- Provide expertise in data analytics, data cluster and data classification;
- Collect data from different sources and create datasets and databases;
- Research and build models for data mining, text mining, recommendation system and machine learning;
- Establish and optimize data structure;
Requirements
- Minimum 1 year experience in data mining, statistic programing and modeling at large scales;
- Being proficient in any of the following languages: R, Python, Java, C/C++, Scala.
- Solid background in recommendation algorithms, experience in machine learning and text mining
- Proven experience in large scale data analytics;
- Fluent English, TOEIC above 600 (or equivalent);
- Background in Computer Science, Statistics, Mathematics or a related Quantitative Discipline.
- 
Preference
- Master Degree in Computer Science, Applied Statistics, Mathematics
- Experience using language processing systems, such as Word segmentation, Automatic Summarization, POS tagging, NER, Topic Modeling, Sentiment analysis…
- Exposure to Search, Analytics base
Experience working with systems such as Hadoop eco system, Spark, Cassandra, Neo4j…
